ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of RICHARD THORPE of Penticton, British Columbia, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of James J.
